ther wizard in our group did.  Mobs wizards DS other mobs.  Should I be using our DS more often in groups, or is it just a waste of mana/aggro/time? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rombusmindspire>Rombus Mindspire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Forum Tyrant<br><br>Owned by Ikeya<BR>Destroying EverWars...<BR><a href=mailto:rombus@graffe.com style=text-decoration: none><u>Contact Rombus</u></font></td></tr></table></span><br>  Posts: 7292<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/16/03 7:20 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Are Our DS line a waste?</span><hr size=1> They're actually semi-useful if you need the extra FR they provide and there's no Mage around.  Other than that though they're fairly useless. <p><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.tritonguild.com/rombus/sig.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:Verdana;font-size:xx-small;">Officer of Triton, Member of Team Ice, Povar<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->:. <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=458434" target="top">Rombus, Arcanist</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> .:. <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=5702" target="top">Rommy, Archon</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> .:<br>
