<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.lotuscult.com">Lotus Cult</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pilsainsilverback>Pilsain Silverback</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 935<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/16/03 7:56 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Are Our DS line a waste?</span><hr size=1> I was just checking on Flickering Flame.  Is a 5pt DS that lasts for 5 minutes for 35mana.  How much damage would it need to do to a mob to be efficient?  Or, does it do so little, that efficiency doesn't matter (Ice Comet vs. Draught argument)?  I'm very intrigued by this, since I haven't really ever thought about it in practice, yet do a lot of cancel magic to mobs in places like Seb that have the same DS on them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=elharinalokhem>Elharina Lokhem</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 364<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/16/03 8:10 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Are Our DS line a waste?</span><hr size=1> Pretty sure flickering flame will do the damage over it's duration to make it damn mana efficient, it's just the arse of memming it hehe. One of the major reasons I had to love this spell has however been nerfed, was nothing like casting it back in early luclin on a ranger to hear their screams with your teeny 5pt damage shield overwriting a good 1k mana's worth of dubiously stacked buffs hehe.<br>
I briefly used the proc off my TOV boots too (other than for making newbies suicide having seen some uber person walk past and buff them) as FR and and extra crap buff when fighting dispellers. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=113259" target="top">Sage Elharina Lokhem 65th Season Wizard</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=114580">Toshimoko Kakita 57th season Monk</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=corinia>Corinia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 76<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/16/03 8:20 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Are Our DS line a waste?</span><hr size=1> Yes, our damage shields are worth it.  I have been using them since I started and that upgraded one that lasts 5 minutes is awesome.  I don't have to cast nearly as much.  My bro can tank more mobs before I have to recast and it does at least 200 hp damage (sometimes more) to some mobs by the time the mob is dead.  That's at least one baby nuke or semi resisted nuke so I'm happy with that.<br>
<br>
Things to know:  our damage shield does not stack with druid or ranger's very well (at least the ranger that I group with prefers his own damage shield and asks me not to cast on him but his damage shield for other people doesn't work so well so he doesn't cast that on others and I damage shield them), we stack very well with mage damage shields.  Another thing to keep in mind is that when mobs are hitting the tank, they are TAKING our damage shield damage even if they are mobs that resist our freaking nukes.<br>
<br>
I generally okeil's levitate myself and use the 5 min damage shield on others. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.questorsmoy.com/eqmemberinfopages/storyrenia/reniasig3.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=davarmagi>DavarMagi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 108<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/16/03 8:23 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Are Our DS line a waste?</span><hr size=1> Flickering flame does not stack with Call of Earth, but it does with the Druid line of DS spells. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=56441">Master Davar Talesian, Arcanist of Tunare</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
Officer of Heretics of the Apocalypse<br>
Torvonnilous<br>
