<br>
Maybe I missed all of the conversations on our DS's back in the day, and this has already been hashed out.  I just don't recall it being talked about, and wondering if maybe we are missing something to our class. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=fqubedf3povar>FqubedF3povar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 168<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/16/03 10:32 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Are Our DS line a waste?</span><hr size=1> Im sure its been talked about because what hasnt. as for aggro I &quot;belive&quot; it has an aggro component. Might help on multi pulls without any CC option, but then agian when that happens the 5pts are gonna do nothing, you either can take them or are casting evac.<br>
<br>
I &quot;have&quot; used them when the tank has no DS on them and its fairly fast pulling but for whatever reason im high mana ill look at pages 30something and mem it. lvl 1s tell you that their alt has a DS thats yada yada yada better and that your DS sucks yadyayadyad, ungratefull twinks.<br>
